{"id": 7720, "title": "Ticket #7720: Complete condor_dagman direct submission and set to default", "description": "<blockquote>\nIn <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=6974\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('6974'); return false;\" title=\"condor_dagman should use submit_utils\">#6974</a></span> we added the ability for condor_dagman to send jobs directly to the schedd using submit_utils, instead of forking condor_submit. Currently it works well but does not support the full range of options that condor_submit does, and is not enabled by default.\n\n<p>We want to add in the missing options and make this the default method for job submission in condor_dagman. These options are all described in <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=6974\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('6974'); return false;\" title=\"condor_dagman should use submit_utils\">#6974</a></span> and I'll probably elaborate on them later in this ticket.</p></blockquote>", "remarks": "<blockquote>\n<em>2020-Dec-04 13:00:30 by coatsworth:</em> <br/>\n\nI am closing this ticket, we are continuing this work in <a class=\"external\" href=\"https://opensciencegrid.atlassian.net/browse/HTCONDOR-112\">https://opensciencegrid.atlassian.net/browse/HTCONDOR-112</a>.</blockquote>", "derived_tickets": "", "attachments": "<html><head></head><body></body></html>", "check_ins": "<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody><tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2020-Aug-25 16:39</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"https://github.com/htcondor/htcondor/commit/f5bb55f14da74210da9f17cf6be1f2f810ad6926\">[60550]</a></span>: direct_condor_submit() now abides by DAGMAN_PROHIBIT_MULTI_JOBS (<span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"abandoned\" href=\"/wiki